name: Hayley Rodgers AET318C Project 4
description: Test your skill in this three-level strategy puzzle game! Maneuver the white block with the arrow/WASD keys and press the SPACEBAR to clone the block. The objective: unlock the next level by triggering all the blue goal cubes simultaneously. Be careful not to fall off the edge of the world or the level will restart! Cycle through levels by pressing "N".
